features: ✔【Product Upgrade】：According to the feedback, our product has been upgraded, all sides are made of polyester fiber, so it is more difficult for small animals to crawl out, but this still requires your supervision.
✔【Perfect Size】：Width & Height after expansion 47 in*15 in (120 cm*38 cm), 10sq.ft， easy to clean.Easy to carry, foldable into a round shape,9.4 in*9.4 in（24cm*24cm）

✔【Suitable range】：suitable for outdoor travel, home use.Suitable for small animals pet playpen, suitable for hamsters, chinchillas, guinea-pigs, mice, gerbils, ferrets, squirrel, bunny, reptile or other small animals.
✔【Easy to Install and Store】: it has the elasticity of the spring, pay attention to keep away from your body and face while opening 6 panels, be careful not to hit others.
✔【EASY to set up and clean】：This playpen is easy to set up and store, and can be rinsed directly with water.
description: It doesn't require complicated assembly, you can immediately create an playpen for your pet. When you need to clean the cage for your pet, you can put the toys in the fence for pets to play. This is a perfect pet playground. You can fill it with toys your pet likes.

After folding, it is the same size as the palm. Fold it up when you don't use it. When you go out with your pet, you can take it in your hand, or put it in your backpack. You can take your pet out to play without worrying about him/ her running around.

Weight: 11oz (About 300g). It's easy to carry and doesn't add any burden to your trip.  High quality, customer satisfaction is our purpose, we hope that customers can use our products satisfactorily and serve customers
